[Episode 8: Hidden in the Mortal World]

14
00:02:09,030 --> 00:02:10,800
I did a lot this morning.

15
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,160
This is the most important.

16
00:02:14,590 --> 00:02:17,520
It took ten lifetimes of merits
for you to fall for me.

17
00:02:18,870 --> 00:02:20,930
Our birthday's engraved in the ring.

18
00:02:21,910 --> 00:02:23,100
Commemorate it properly.

19
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:26,500
[0930]

20
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:30,560
It's mainly to formally
express my feelings.

21
00:02:50,750 --> 00:02:51,950
Why won't you wear it?

22
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,570
Let's wait till Monday.

23
00:02:57,750 --> 00:02:58,360
Okay.

24
00:02:59,150 --> 00:02:59,750
Monday.

25
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,970
After this bridge and a right turn,
we'll be home.

26
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,150
Shall we cross it?

27
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,740
Let's get some fresh air
at the end of the bridge.

28
00:03:51,750 --> 00:03:54,079
Fleeting encounters with various people

29
00:03:54,590 --> 00:03:56,079
led to my meeting with you.

30
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,860
From now on, it's only you.

31
00:04:04,910 --> 00:04:06,240
Our secret.

32
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:08,150
No one in this city

33
00:04:08,910 --> 00:04:10,750
can find out we're together.

34
00:04:16,630 --> 00:04:17,680
Just in case...

35
00:04:19,070 --> 00:04:19,930
In case of what?

36
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,920
Count from this pipe towards that way.

37
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,010
How many would be good luck?

38
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,600
How many?

39
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,780
I'm asking you.

40
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:39,650
Maybe three?

41
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,750
No, seven.

42
00:04:46,270 --> 00:04:48,240
In case I lose you someday,

43
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:52,270
write a note and put it
inside this steel pipe.

44
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,870
Tell me when to come
and wait for you here.

45
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:57,870
You won't lose me.

46
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,720
Our shadows are the same.

47
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:14,240
Maybe our absence

48
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:16,870
will not

49
00:05:18,360 --> 00:05:19,680
change a thing

50
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:21,160
in this city.

51
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,160
Then...

52
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:28,630
What if you log off?

53
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:31,560
Leave a message in that pipe too

54
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,240
so I can find you.

55
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,000
Okay.

56
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:40,630
Let's go home.

57
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:43,890
Let's go.

58
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:55,040
Want to take a look

59
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,500
at something in the trunk?

60
00:05:57,390 --> 00:05:58,159
What is it?

61
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,410
It's for you.

62
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,250
Let's go home first.

63
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:05,190
Take a look.

64
00:06:29,630 --> 00:06:31,430
Didn't I accomplish a lot today?

65
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,620
How are you?

66
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:50,270
Are you okay?

67
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:51,750
Any discomfort?

68
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:05,720
I feel fine.

69
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,240
This was the longest session.

70
00:10:13,000 --> 00:10:13,790
How long?

71
00:10:15,630 --> 00:10:17,360
3 hours and 40 minutes.

72
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,440
It's noon.

73
00:10:31,510 --> 00:10:32,710
Come have some water.

74
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:38,840
Sit.

75
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,290
Fill in the form after.

76
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:55,080
Don't exaggerate your feelings,

77
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,880
but don't downplay them either.

78
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,800
Write according to how you feel.

79
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:07,760
What's wrong?

80
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:13,120
This pen is out of ink.

81
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,180
How could it be?

82
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:18,310
It'll be soon.

83
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:22,120
I've been using this pen for months.

84
00:11:33,750 --> 00:11:35,280
For the highlighted parts,

85
00:11:35,390 --> 00:11:36,840
take note to exclude any medication

86
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,570
or physiological influences.

87
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:42,100
[Assessment Form]

88
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:40,340
[Xu Tian (Male, 32), 1993.09.30, Libra]

89
00:11:42,510 --> 00:11:44,370
I've filled this in so many times.

90
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:46,000
Who has?

91
00:11:48,320 --> 00:11:48,910
Me.

92
00:11:50,910 --> 00:11:51,790
Xu Tian.

93
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:06,750
This morning when you came for hypnosis,

94
00:12:06,750 --> 00:12:08,280
you were still Jia Xiaoduo.

95
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:23,020
Will she come back?

96
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:25,340
[Prefers sneakers, pants, no makeup]

97
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:29,080
She won't.

98
00:12:31,390 --> 00:12:32,320
How do you know?

99
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,270
I'm a doctor.

100
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:44,440
So, can I be discharged?

101
00:12:45,510 --> 00:12:46,200
Of course.

102
00:12:47,080 --> 00:12:48,200
Anytime you wish.

103
00:12:48,960 --> 00:12:49,720
I told you

104
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:51,730
this is not a prison.

105
