[Q. An alter only has one emotion.
A. Mostly Agree/Agree]

106
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:10,460
[Q. When you're sad, a voice comforts you.
A. Sometimes/Not Sure]

107
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,000
You altered some.

108
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:15,080
Which?

109
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:21,550
When you come to this world
with the assessment form,

110
00:13:21,550 --> 00:13:23,950
