you lost your superpowers?

111
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:26,360
No.

112
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:28,630
Do you think an alter

113
00:13:28,630 --> 00:13:29,760
only has one emotion

114
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,570
