115
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:35,200
Yes.

116
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,890
When you're extremely sad,

117
00:13:38,270 --> 00:13:40,390
a voice seems to comfort you

118
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,670
or you feel like

119
00:13:42,000 --> 00:13:43,930
