122
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,160
Do you feel it?

123
00:14:04,390 --> 00:14:06,320
I don't feel any sadness at all.

124
00:14:08,390 --> 00:14:11,000
So why do I need a voice to comfort me?

125
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,510
I don't need to be embraced either.

126
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,600
Very good.

127
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:33,550
You once told me...

128
00:14:36,120 --> 00:14:37,870
not to expel Jia Xiaoduo.

129
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,360
But you still did it.

130
00:14:44,510 --> 00:14:46,030
You requested for it.

131
00:14:48,200 --> 00:14:49,870
Isn't that why you came here?

132
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,600
Have I ever changed my mind?

133
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:57,790
Have a change of heart?

134
00:15:05,550 --> 00:15:06,080
No.

135
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:13,580
This form was

136
00:15:13,580 --> 00:15:14,960
[Assessment Form: Jia Xiaoduo]

137
00:15:14,960 --> 00:15:16,360
filled in by Jia Xiaoduo.

138
00:15:18,270 --> 00:15:19,360
At that time,

139
00:15:19,720 --> 00:15:21,080
you had five alters.

140
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:23,080
Yu Dan, the surgeon,

141
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,200
Tie Lin, the delivery agent,

142
00:15:25,200 --> 00:15:27,130
Wang Yangming, the motorcyclist,

143
00:15:27,240 --> 00:15:28,910
Liu Tiao'er, the dieter,

144
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:31,660
and Jia Xiaoduo, the strongest among them.

145
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:32,600
[Assessment Form: Jia Xiaoduo]

146
00:15:32,600 --> 00:15:35,260
She even believed
she was the primary identity,

147
00:15:35,630 --> 00:15:37,630
with an inclination to replace you.

148
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:40,750
Replace me?

149
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:43,600
Usually,

150
00:15:43,600 --> 00:15:44,660
